            <description><![CDATA[【<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3%E5%9C%B0%E9%93%81%E4%B8%80%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E7%AA%81%E5%8F%91%E7%8C%9D%E6%AD%BB%E5%9E%8B%E5%BF%83%E6%A2%97%E6%99%95%E5%80%92%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3%E5%9C%B0%E9%93%81%E4%B8%80%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E7%AA%81%E5%8F%91%E7%8C%9D%E6%AD%BB%E5%9E%8B%E5%BF%83%E6%A2%97%E6%99%95%E5%80%92%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#深圳地铁一男子突发猝死型心梗晕倒#</span></a> AED又救人一命<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[心]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/l_xin-43af9086c0.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】近日，深圳一男子乘坐地铁时突发心梗晕倒在车厢，无意识，无自主呼吸！乘客第一时间联系了地铁司机，并拨打120。地铁工作人员立刻使用AED救助，将乘客从“死神”手里拽回！检查发现，男子经历的是非常危险的猝死型心梗。几年里，<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1AED%E5%B7%B2%E6%88%90%E5%8A%9F%E6%8C%BD%E5%9B%9E82%E6%9D%A1%E7%94%9F%E5%91%BD%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1AED%E5%B7%B2%E6%88%90%E5%8A%9F%E6%8C%BD%E5%9B%9E82%E6%9D%A1%E7%94%9F%E5%91%BD%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#深圳公共AED已成功挽回82条生命#</span></a>。 <span class="url-icon"><img alt="[赞啊]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/lxh/lxh_zana-dd20c7bed2.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4993772602195976" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">第一现场的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/orj480/6aac5feagy1hm4vzj24noj21hc0u0go2.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/u0/c7iXjrTcgx08bZMUtAjK01041201ch6C0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1706283087&amp;ssig=SdcnLpqb7V&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/u0/93yhzH89gx08bZMSLrIA01041200EBN60E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1706283087&amp;ssig=POIwmMZtCK&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/u0/QNnUXgsZgx08bZMSRRn201041200qpJt0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=640x360.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1706283087&amp;ssig=KvY%2FoxIfrt&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A4993772602195976" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
